MAE vs Alternative Metrics Decision Matrix

| Metric | Outlier Sensitivity | Unit           | Business Use             |
| ------ | ------------------- | -------------- | ------------------------ |
| MAE    | Low                 | Same as target | Budgeting, forecasting   |
| MSE    | High                | Squared        | Model optimization       |
| RMSE   | High                | Same as target | Penalty for large errors |
| MAPE   | Medium              | Percentage     | Relative accuracy        |


Production Guidelines:


Salary prediction: MAE (direct ₹ impact)
Revenue forecast:  MAPE (growth con)
Energy demand:     RMSE (safety-critical)

